 s FREE\, All Ages Event. Space is Limited.\n\nAbout the Band:\n\nThe Dict
 ator Tots are dedicated to playing Jammy Prog Shite. Based in Petaluma\, 
 they focus on original material and creative improvisation. The Tots are 
 Pete Hale-Guit/Voc\, Steve Hoffman/Toby Tyler-Bass\, Brad Hoffman/Sean En
 gland-Drums\, Bob McBain-Keys
