DESCRIPTION:Therapy Dog Wellness Hours at the Disability Cultural Center  
 Need a moment to de-stress\, smile\, and soak up some puppy love this spri
 ng? Come join us for Therapy Dog Wellness Hours at the SRJC Disability Cul
 tural Center!  Spend time with certified therapy dogs\, enjoy their calmin
 g energy\, and leave feeling a little more grounded and recharged.Event de
 tails:Disability Cultural Center    Santa Rosa Campus\, Bertolini Student 
 Center\, 3rd Floor Landing  12–1 PM  Free and open to all SRJC students\
 , staff\, and community members!    Visit the DCC Website here (https://dr
 d.santarosa.edu/dcc)!
