 Disability Cultural Center</strong></p><p>  Need a moment to de-stress\, s
 mile\, and soak up some puppy love this spring? Come join us for Therapy D
 og Wellness Hours at the SRJC Disability Cultural Center!</p><p>  Spend ti
 me with certified therapy dogs\, enjoy their calming energy\, and leave fe
 eling a little more grounded and recharged.</p><p><strong>Event details:</
 strong></p><ul><li>Disability Cultural Center<br />    Santa Rosa Campus\,
  Bertolini Student Center\, 3rd Floor Landing  </li><li>12–1 PM  </li><l
 i>Free and open to all SRJC students\, staff\, and community members!  </l
 i></ul><p>  Visit the <a href="https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc" target="_bla
 nk" rel="noopener">DCC Website here</a>!</p>
