DESCRIPTION:Nicole Irene Anderson creates psychological\, ambiguous compos
 itions that respond to specific locations and lived experiences. Anderson 
 earned an M.F.A. in Art Studio from the University of California\, Davis\,
  and a B.F.A. in Painting/Drawing from California College of the Arts in S
 an Francisco.  For more information\, visit SRJC's Agrella Art Gallery web
 site! (https://art-gallery.santarosa.edu/exhibition/visiting-artist-lectur
 e-series-spring-2026)  You can see more of her work on her website here! (
 https://www.nicoleireneanderson.com/%C2%A0)
