 f California\, Davis\, and a B.F.A. in Painting/Drawing from California Co
 llege of the Arts in San Francisco.</p><p>  For more information\, visit <
 a href="https://art-gallery.santarosa.edu/exhibition/visiting-artist-lectu
 re-series-spring-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SRJC's Agrella Art G
 allery website!</a></p><p>  You can see more of her work on <a href="https
