SUMMARY:Candlelight Yoga @ Hotel Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:Nourish 108 Ayurveda & Yoga\nJoin me for 60 minutes of nourish
 ing de-stress yoga by candlelight in the Brooklyn Ballroom (upstairs) at H
 otel Petaluma. Please bring your own mat and any props you might need (blo
 ck\, strap\, bolster strap\, blanket)\, and arrive a few minutes early to 
 get situated.\n\nAll levels welcome!\n\nDrop in is $18\, class passes are 
 available. FREE for hotel guests.\nSign up through the calendar at [www.no
 urish108.com/classes](www.nourish108.com/classes) or at the front desk if 
 you're a guest. Credit/debit in advance\, cash/Venmo on site.\n\nI look fo
 rward to practicing with you!🧘🏻‍♀️🕯️
