SUMMARY:Figure Drawing Night at Suite G Studio!
DESCRIPTION:Petaluma Figure Drawing Meetup Group\nJoin us for an evening o
 f creativity and inspiration at the Petaluma Figure Drawing Meetup Group's
  Figure Drawing Night at Suite G Studio! Whether you're a seasoned artist 
 or just starting out\, this event is the perfect opportunity to hone your 
 skills\, meet fellow artists\, and immerse yourself in the world of figura
 tive painting. Our life drawing sessions are open to artists and art lover
 s of all levels\, so don't be shy to join us and express your creativity o
 n paper. We provide a supportive and encouraging environment where everyon
 e can feel comfortable exploring their artistic talents.\n\n[BECOME A MEMB
 ER](https://www.suitegstudio.com/artist-resources) of Suite G Studio for $
 40/month. Or RSVP by sending $25 to @suiteg on Venmo or email suitegstudio
 620@gmail.com\n\nBe prepared for an evening filled with sketching\, painti
 ng\, and drawing as we focus on capturing the human form in all its beauty
  and complexity. This event is a great opportunity to practice your figure
  drawing techniques and unleash your artistic potential. Whether you prefe
 r using pencils\, charcoal\, pastels\, or paint\, there's something for ev
 eryone at our Figure Drawing Night. Come and be a part of our community of
  artists dedicated to celebrating and expressing the beauty of life throug
 h art.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/petaluma-figure-drawing-meetup-group/
 events/313760335/
