ATTACH:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/live/image/gid/3/width/80/height/80/
 crop/1/src_region/0,0,497,497/229_WHM-Logo-2024-JH_500x500.rev.1738968772.
 png
CATEGORIES:Awareness Months,Department Events
DESCRIPTION:Presenter: Denise BeesonJoin the Zoom here! (https://santarosa
 -edu.zoom.us/j/87117554258)&#160\;  Meeting ID: 871 1755 4258Event Descrip
 tion: How many of your genealogy search challenges involve Female ancestor
 s? Knowing our Female ancestors hinges upon knowing her maiden name\, but 
 there are few records of her\, and almost none that contain her maiden nam
 e. Believe it or not\, there's no record set that even focuses specificall
 y on women! So\, you need to be strategic in your search. Join me to learn
  how to find your Female ancestor(s)!  For more information\, visit SRJC's
  Women's History Month website (https://events.santarosa.edu/womxns-histor
 y-month-2026).
LAST-MODIFIED:20260312T215904Z
LOCATION:Zoom
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/16533-finding-women-in-historical
 -records
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Presenter: Denise Beeson</p><p><a href="
 https://santarosa-edu.zoom.us/j/87117554258" target="_blank" rel="noopener
 ">Join the Zoom here!</a>&#160\;</p><p>  Meeting ID: 871 1755 4258</p><p><
 strong>Event Description</strong>: How many of your genealogy search chall
 enges involve Female ancestors? Knowing our Female ancestors hinges upon k
 nowing her maiden name\, but there are few records of her\, and almost non
 e that contain her maiden name. Believe it or not\, there's no record set 
 that even focuses specifically on women! So\, you need to be strategic in 
 your search. Join me to learn how to find your Female ancestor(s)!</p><p> 
  For more information\, visit <a href="https://events.santarosa.edu/womxns
 -history-month-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SRJC's Women's History
  Month website</a>.</p>
