 w Thing!\n\nBarry's New Thing is a collection of friends making music in 
 Petaluma. The band plays a broad range of fun covers\, including songs fr
 om:\nSupertramp\, Elton John\, Beatles\, Police\, Fleetwood Mac\, CSNY\, 
 Hank Williams\, Elvis\, Roy Orbison\, Turtles\, Steely Dan\, Bee Gees\, J
 oe Cocker\, Ray Charles\, Grateful Dead\, Eurhythmics\, Buddy Holly\, Eag
 les\, REM\, Secret Sisters\, Abigail Lapell and many more. Featuring: Bar
 ry Bisson on keyboard\, guitar & vocals\, Tony Blake on drums\, Perry Sav
 as on bass\, Tim Jenkins on guitar\, Mary Lindsay and Carol Oppenheimer o
 n vocals. And as always\, a few special guests!
