SUMMARY:Blossoms at Japanese Tea Garden 🌸
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nSpring is in full bloom and we able to
  experience Sakura season right here at home. We'll grab some tea and walk
  through to snap some pictures of the bright fuschia azaleas as well as Ch
 erry and plum blossoms in peak bloom right now.\n\nThis is a special event
  with timed entry\, so I am purchasing tickets as a group for a lower rate
  of $16.50 each. My Venmo is @A-Richard. Please DM me if RSVPing later tha
 n Wednesday 3/25 to see if I still have tickets available. I am cross post
 ing event in other groups\, so attendees list may fluctuate. Happy to make
  reservation to try local restaurant for those who are interested that is 
 in walking distance. Please state interest in comments by this Wednesday. 
 Thanks\n\nGG Park can be busy on wknds so please plan ahead in looking for
  parking. I'm happy to carpool from Petaluma or Marin County if anyone in 
 interested\, but I will be staying for a bite afterwards.
