SUMMARY:English Country Dance Sebastopol Advanced
DESCRIPTION:North Bay Contra Dance\nOur 5th Sunday series is for experienc
 ed dancers\, so instruction will be streamlined and the dances will be mor
 e complex than at our 1st and 3rd Sunday dances. We expect dancers attendi
 ng these sessions to be completely comfortable with heys for 3 and 4\, dol
 phin heys\, figure 8s\, and triple minor progression. They should also be 
 able to maintain their sense of orientation within the set. This is not th
 e time to bring your friends who are new to English country dancing\, thou
 gh we’d love to see them at the 1st and 3rd Sundays.\n\nThe regular EC d
 ance is held the 1st and 3rd Sundays of each month\, 2-4:30 pm\, to live m
 usic\, all levels of experience welcome\; and occasional 5th Sundays for A
 dvanced dancers. Admission is $15 for members of NBCDS and its affiliates\
 , $8 for young adults ages 19-30\, and $3 for youth ages 6 – 18.
