SUMMARY:Inner Body Guided-Meditation (20 minutes)
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\n"Awareness of the inner body takes yo
 u beyond the mind." - Eckhart Tolle\n\nIn this mediation session we will b
 ring our attention here: to the inner body. Sessions are suitable for newc
 omers\, those experienced in Tolle's teachings and anyone wishing to remai
 n completely anonymous. They will last around 20 minutes and cameras and m
 icrophones will be disabled.\n(Depending on the situation\, a free discuss
 ion may be held at the end with mics and cameras allowed.)\n\nSee you ther
 e!\n\nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Katie online mediation gro
 up. Visit [this Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree
 /) for more information.\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no
  members have joined after 10 minutes.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/events/313737930/
