DESCRIPTION:Exhibit Dates: April 1st - May 31st\, 2026  Opening Reception 
 Friday\, April 3rd\, 1:00 - 3:00 pm  This exhibit features both traditiona
 l and non-traditional arts of Indigenous SRJC students from many different
  tribal backgrounds\, including painting\, drawing\, beadwork\, ceramics\,
  textiles and sculpture. Join us in the Museum on Friday\, April 3rd for a
  casual reception. Meet the artists and enjoy a light snack.  For more inf
 ormation\, visit SRJC's Multicultural Museum Website! (https://museum.sant
 arosa.edu/event/honoring-ancestry)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T204626Z
