 26<br />  Opening Reception Friday\, April 3rd\, 1:00 - 3:00 pm<br />  Thi
 s exhibit features both traditional and non-traditional arts of Indigenous
  SRJC students from many different tribal backgrounds\, including painting
 \, drawing\, beadwork\, ceramics\, textiles and sculpture. Join us in the 
 Museum on Friday\, April 3rd for a casual reception. Meet the artists and 
 enjoy a light snack.</p><p>  For more information\, visit <a href="https:/
 /museum.santarosa.edu/event/honoring-ancestry" target="_blank" rel="noopen
 er">SRJC's Multicultural Museum Website!</a></p>
