ATTACH:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/live/image/gid/1/width/80/height/80/
 crop/1/src_region/0,0,2400,3200/418_IMG_9377.rev.1757006958.jpg
CATEGORIES:District Events,Student Services
DESCRIPTION:The Free Farmer's Market is located outside\, under the outdoo
 r canopy\, between buildings 400 &amp\; 500.  For faster check-in\, downlo
 ad the "MySRJC App" and register with Redwood Empire Food Bank prior to th
 e event.  Don't forget to bring your own grocery bags\, some will be provi
 ded on a first come first serve basis.  Can't make it? Leftover produce an
