SUMMARY:Book Club - Hope in the Dark
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T013000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T030000
UID:e5ebc1dd2b090bb477388e2097ef8cd3@coolpetaluma.org
DESCRIPTION:Cool Petaluma Book Club Our book for April\, Hope in the Dark 
 by Rebecca Solnit\, shows us why we should not give up hope\, even though 
 our future is uncertain. In fact\, we should be committed to it in all its
  unknowability. PLEASE NOTE: There are 5 copies at Copperfield’s\; ask f
 or one at the counter. Let them know you’re with the Cool Petaluma Clima
 te Book Club. Plus\, get 10% off! #block-48fda9e02d14584b80b1 { --tweak-te
 xt-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px\; --tweak-text-block-radius: unset\; --st
 roke-style: none\;--stroke-thickness: 6px\; --tweak-text-block-stroke-colo
 r: var(--tweak-text-block-stroke-color)\;border-width: unset\; border-styl
 e: unset\; border-color: unset\; background-color: unset\;}#block-48fda9e0
 2d14584b80b1 .sqs-html-content { --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%\;
  padding: unset\;}#block-48fda9e02d14584b80b1 { mix-blend-mode: var(--twea
 k-text-block-blend )\; } #block-48fda9e02d14584b80b1 { } RSVP Here #block-
 41ef93226c8a0444c843 {--sqs-block-content-flex: 0\; } Hope in the Dark Sol
 nit’s book is a manifesto for hope in place of the despair that engulfs 
 many activists when their campaigns to make the world a better place or sa
 feguard local values from globalized corporations do not bear immediate fr
 uit. Solnit advocates for embracing the darkness of an uncertain future an
 d campaigning from the perspective that previously unforeseen changes are 
 always possible. In this book\, she seeks to safeguard against the cultura
 l amnesia in which people forget that previously unthinkable events change
 d history\, such as obtaining suffrage for women after millennia of patria
 rchy. In addition\, she emphasizes that no easy cause-and-effect relations
 hip exists between activism and seeing changes realized. Instead\, the pat
 h to change twists and turns\, with many defeats as well as small victorie
 s. #block-5ce66d8084f2469abf99 { --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0p
 x\; --tweak-text-block-radius: unset\; --stroke-style: none\;--stroke-thic
 kness: 6px\; --tweak-text-block-stroke-color: var(--tweak-text-block-strok
