BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Petaluma Chamber of Commerce": "https://business.petalumachamber.us/events/details/free-estate-planning-webinar-04-08-2026"}
X-SOURCE-ID:petaluma_chamber
SUMMARY:Free Estate Planning Webinar
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T183000
UID:d4c328542e1f8d88093eb44e8652a2a1@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Details Strategies to Manage Incapacity\, Family Dynamics\, an
 d Financial Risks Creating your estate plan\, whether it’s a living trus
 t or a will\, can be a daunting task. Estate planning addresses issues tha
 t are difficult to think about\, such as death\, incapacity\, finances\, a
 nd family dynamics. It can be easy to procrastinate\, even though these is
 sues may weigh heavily on your mind. We invite you to attend one of our up
 coming free webinars so you can take the first step toward having peace of
  mind by creating (or updating) your estate plan. This is an educational w
 ebinar\, where we highlight some of the concerns that many families face a
 nd how an estate plan can help. The attorneys also break down how wills an
 d trusts differ\, and some of the common estate planning pitfalls and how 
 to avoid them. Our goal is to provide you with the education you need to p
 rotect yourself and your family\, and leave a legacy of peace. If you woul
 d like to set up a meeting to discuss your estate planning needs
LOCATION:Petaluma\, CA
URL:https://business.petalumachamber.us/events/details/free-estate-plannin
 g-webinar-04-08-2026
X-SOURCE:Petaluma Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
