SUMMARY:Vital Information About Wills\, Trusts\, and Estate Plans
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T183000
UID:f857b9f46183ca0d0e6deef7884ecb72@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Strategies to Manage Incapacity\, Family Dynamics\, and Financ
 ial Risks Creating your estate plan\, whether it’s a living trust or a w
 ill\, can be a daunting task. Estate planning addresses issues that are di
 fficult to think about\, such as death\, incapacity\, finances\, and famil
 y dynamics. It can be easy to procrastinate\, even though these issues may
  weigh heavily on your mind. We invite you to attend one of our upcoming f
 ree webinars so you can take the first step toward having peace of mind by
  creating (or updating) your estate plan. This is an educational webinar\,
  where we highlight some of the concerns that many families face and how a
 n estate plan can help. The attorneys also break down how wills and trusts
  differ\, and some of the common estate planning pitfalls and how to avoid
  them. Our goal is to provide you with the education you need to protect y
 ourself and your family\, and leave a legacy of peace. If you would like t
 o set up a meeting to discuss your estate planning needs further
LOCATION:Petaluma\, CA
URL:https://business.petalumachamber.us/events/details/vital-information-a
 bout-wills-trusts-and-estate-plans
X-SOURCE:Petaluma Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Rebel Craft Collective": "https://www.meetup.com/the-rebel-craft-collective/events/313260344/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_the_rebel_craft_collective
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Rebel Craft Collective
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/the-rebel-craft-collective/
UID:event_313260344@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260323T025116Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T193000
SUMMARY:Happy Hour Crafts
DESCRIPTION:The Rebel Craft Collective\nWine + tasty snacks + your latest 
 project and a friendly group of likeminded crafters... what better way to 
 unwind? Come join us!\n\nThis is a relaxed\, drop-in-friendly event. Come 
 when you can\, leave when you must. Newcomers and occasional-comers are al
 ways welcome!\n\n**What do we mean by “crafts”?**\nWhatever “craft
 ” means to you! And whatever is portable enough to bring to a wine bar. 
 Knitting\, crochet\, and other fiber arts are most common\, but we have al
 so warmly welcomed people who sketch\, color\, embroider\, bead\, and more
 . If your craft isn’t portable\, we will happily ooh and aah over photos
  of your work-in-progress\, or chat about your plans for your next project
 .\n\n**Health & Safety**\nMasks are very welcome\, and nobody will pressur
 e you to eat or drink. If the weather is nice\, we will try to sit outside
 . If you aren’t eating/drinking during the event\, please consider order
 ing some of La Dolce Vita’s delicious food to-go\, in order to help supp
 ort our gracious\, long-time venue.\n\n**Parking**\nParking in downtown Pe
 taluma is free\, but street parking has a strictly enforced 2 hour limit u
 ntil 6pm. To park for longer\, try the nearest garage:\n\n* The Second Str
 eet Garage entrance is located on C Street between First and Second Street
 s. It's all day parking on every level and a short walk to La Dolce Vita.\
 n\n**Ages**\nIt's a wine bar\, so this event is for adult crafters (though
  you're certainly not required to drink wine!). We’re okay with babes-in
 -arms if you are\, but this is not the right setting for wee crafters who 
 are moving about on their own.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-rebel-craft-collective/events/313
 260344/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260208T041752Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260208T041752Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
