SUMMARY:Petaluma Safety & Wellbeing Series: Social Media Safety & Crisis Prevention
DESCRIPTION:Join us at 6pm for a FREE dinner from Jersey Mike's Subs\, and learn more about these vital resources! \nSocial Media Safety director\, Lyn Romstad\, will be teaming up with Mario Castillo\, a Community Outreach Education Coordinator with Buckelew’s 988 Suicide Prevention\, for a public presentation at the Theater on April 23! This is the next of PKF’s ongoing Petaluma Community Wellbeing Series presentations in collaboration with other subject matter expert organizations to bring you a free resource to promote safety\, health\, and wellbeing in our community.
