 , R&B\, and soul into a feel-good sound perfected from Texas blues joints
  to New Orleans funk halls. This Sonoma County favorite has recorded 10 a
 lbums and delivers high-energy improvisation!\nWho's Cooking: Momo Man\nW
 hen: Saturday\, April 26th\, 2-6pm\nWhere: Griffo Distillery & Tasting Ba
 r\nRSVP's are encouraged for this FREE\, All Ages Event. Space is Limited
 .
