 ngers-on-a-train-a-stopstar
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The Petaluma Cinema Series is a film edu
 cation program that brings together SRJC film students\, the campus commun
 ity\, and Sonoma County residents to engage in dialogue around classic\, f
 oreign\, &amp\; independent films. Presentations feature SRJC film faculty
 \, industry guests\, interdisciplinary experts\, and technical demonstrati
 ons. All evenings include post-screening discussions.</p><ul><li>Pre-film 
 program: 6pm  </li><li>Film screening: 7pm (longer run times begin at 6:30
 pm)  </li><li>Post-screening discussion until 10pm  </li></ul><p>  For mor
 e information\, visit: <a href="https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cinema-se
 ries/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cin
 ema-series/</a>&#160\;</p>
