BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-ID:gcal_c_69dcaa6c13b06c1111a1706565ebb272c3d24290c650a9378bdbd37bff886879
SUMMARY:Vintage Camper Trailer Magazine - Petaluma Rallie Progressive Wine
  Stroll
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260501T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260501T170000
DTSTAMP:20260323T025144Z
UID:6id3p3roiflefpj3o3lh78kebd@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260501T140000
SEQUENCE:0
CREATED:20260225T153103Z
DESCRIPTION:<h2><strong>Sip\, Stroll &amp\; Stay Funky: The Petaluma Ralli
 e Progressive Tasting</strong> 🍷🚐</h2><p>Park the trailer and grab y
 our walking shoes! Immerse yourself in the soulful\, artistic heart of dow
 ntown Petaluma with an exclusive progressive wine path curated specificall
 y for the <strong>Vintage Camper Trailer Magazine's Petaluma Rallie</stron
 g>.</p><p>Experience the <strong>historic charm</strong> of our river town
 —where Victorian architecture meets a vibrant\, modern art scene—as yo
 u wander between three of Petaluma's most celebrated\, award-winning tasti
 ng rooms. All three locations are situated within a short\, scenic stroll 
 of one another.</p><hr /><h3><strong>The Award-Winning Lineup:</strong></h
 3><ul><li><p><strong><a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://www.
 brooksnote.com/" target="_blank">Brooks Note Winery</a>:</strong> Industri
 al chic\, soulful\, and family-owned\, focusing on the best of the Petalum
 a Gap.</p></li><li><p><strong><a href="https://adoberoadwines.com/" target
 ="_blank">Adobe Road Winery</a>:</strong> High-octane luxury and world-cla
 ss craftsmanship in a stunning waterfront setting.</p></li><li><p><strong>
 <a href="https://www.russewines.com/" target="_blank">Montagne Russe Winer
 y</a>:</strong> A funky\, small-batch urban winery and record lounge where
  art and wine collide.</p></li></ul><hr /><h3><strong>The Details:</strong
 ></h3><ul><li><p><strong>When:</strong> Friday\, May 1 | 2\;00 PM – 5:00
  PM</p></li><li><p><strong>What:</strong> A curated flight of <strong>3 aw
 ard-winning wines</strong> at <strong>each</strong> location (9 wines tota
 l!).</p></li><li><p><strong>Vibe:</strong> Uniquely Petaluma. Think indust
 rial-chic galleries\, historic storefronts\, and world-class cool-climate 
 pours.</p></li><li><p><strong>Cost:</strong> <strong>$60 per person</stron
 g> for the full three-winery circuit.</p></li></ul><p>Don't just visit Pet
 aluma—taste the creative spirit that makes us the most inspired corner o
 f wine country. Grab your rally mates and come celebrate the art of the po
 ur!</p><p>Purchase Tickets <a href="https://www.brooksnotewinery.com/produ
 ct/vct-petaluma-rallie-progressive-wine-stroll">Here:</a>  </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T153345Z
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-SOURCE:Petaluma Community Center
X-SOURCE-URL:https://petalumacommunity.org/
END:VEVENT
