SUMMARY: Family Open Mic Night
DESCRIPTION:Join us on the first Friday of each month for a fun\, family-
 friendly open mic for musicians 18 and under (can be accompanied on stage
  by 18+). Sign-ups start at 4:30pm\, with performances from 5–6pm. Local 
 music teachers Julia Cramer and Tyler Johnson will host and provide optio
