BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"The Big Easy": "https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/feather-and-flow-starring-coco-lamarr-and-lbz-band/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bigeasy
X-SOURCE:The Big Easy
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260502T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260502T213000
DTSTAMP:20260308T185710
CREATED:20260212T193807Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260212T193807Z
UID:10002552-1777750200-1777757400@bigeasypetaluma.com
SUMMARY:Feather and Flow: Starring Coco Lamarr and LBZ & Band
DESCRIPTION:The last show was such a success we are going to do it again! Save the date for May 2nd. \nThotty McNaughty presents an evening of classic Live Jazz From Award-Winning Cabaret Chanteuse Coco Lamarr. In 2021\, Coco was awarded Best Vocalist and Best Film at the Hollywood & Southern California Burlesque Film Festival. In July 2024\, Coco won first place at The Battle of The Ballads singing competition at Juliet Cocktail Room inside the Venetian Casino & Resort. And in 2025\, she launched The Winehouse Revival\, a soul-soaked\, immersive tribute show celebrating the music and legacy of Amy Winehouse\, which has quickly become a highlight of California’s live music and cabaret scene. \nCoco will be backed by LBZ and band. LaiddBackZach (LBZ)\, is a North Bay/Bay Area R&B\, Hip-Hop\, Funk\, & Soul artist known for energetic shows with his band\, often performing in Sonoma County venues like the Luther Burbank Center for the Arts\, The California Theater\, The Big Easy and breweries\, blending songwriting with funk and soul grooves. You will also enjoy orginal pieces from LBZ and his band intermixed with Coco’s jazz covers for dazzling Burlesque performers. \nTickets coming soon!
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/feather-and-flow-starring-coco-lamarr-and-lbz-band/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
CATEGORIES:Burlesque
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Feather-and-flow2.png
END:VEVENT
