DESCRIPTION:The Petaluma Cinema Series is a film education program that br
 ings together SRJC film students\, the campus community\, and Sonoma Count
 y residents to engage in dialogue around classic\, foreign\, &amp\; indepe
 ndent films. Presentations feature SRJC film faculty\, industry guests\, i
 nterdisciplinary experts\, and technical demonstrations. All evenings incl
 ude post-screening discussions.Pre-film program: 6pm  Film screening: 7pm 
 (longer run times begin at 6:30pm)  Post-screening discussion until 10pm  
   For more information\, visit: https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cinema-se
 ries/ (https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cinema-series/)&#160\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20260204T003650Z
LOCATION:Carole L. Ellis Auditorium - Petaluma Campus
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/14434-petaluma-cinema-series-daze
 d-and-confused
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The Petaluma Cinema Series is a film edu
 cation program that brings together SRJC film students\, the campus commun
 ity\, and Sonoma County residents to engage in dialogue around classic\, f
 oreign\, &amp\; independent films. Presentations feature SRJC film faculty
 \, industry guests\, interdisciplinary experts\, and technical demonstrati
 ons. All evenings include post-screening discussions.</p><ul><li>Pre-film 
 program: 6pm  </li><li>Film screening: 7pm (longer run times begin at 6:30
 pm)  </li><li>Post-screening discussion until 10pm  </li></ul><p>  For mor
 e information\, visit: <a href="https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cinema-se
 ries/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cin
 ema-series/</a>&#160\;</p>
