SUMMARY: Scott Street Gin Jam: 1st & 3rd Thursdays EVERY Month
DESCRIPTION:Join us every other Thursday for a Jam like no other!\n\n🎶 S
 cott Street Gin Jam at Griffo Distillery! 🎶\n\nJoin us EVERY 1st & 3rd T
 hursday at Griffo Distillery for the Scott Street Gin Jam! The Griffo jam
  is unlike any other and we want YOU to be a part of it! Doors open at 5p
 m\, just in time to grab a cocktail\, a seat\, or load in your gear befor
 e the jam starts at 6pm!\n\nAll ages\, all skill levels\, and all genres 
 welcome! Whether you play\, sing\, or just want to kick back with a cockt
 ail and soak in the http://vibes...this http://vibes...this vibes...this 
 is the best way to spend your Thursday!\n\nPLUS\, we've got "8 dolla holl
 a cocktails" ALL NIGHT LONG!\n\nMusicians: Bring your own instrument and 
 amp if you have a preferred setup. Bring your pedals\, http://horns...any
 thing http://horns...anything horns...anything you've got or hop on our h
 ouse drum kit\, grab the mic and let's rock and roll!\n\nEveryone else: C
 ome grab a seat and watch the magic unfold! Bring your energy\, your frie
 nds\, your moves and get ready to dance your way into the weekend!\n\nHun
 gry?! We've got you covered! Every 3rd Thursday our resident Grill Master
 \, Ryan pulls his rig out to the patio\, fires up the coals\, and throws 
 down for our Community BBQ & Potluck! Bring a side to share\, something t
 o throw on the grill\, or your generosity for the tip jar - 'cuz wait til
 l you try his http://ribs...and http://ribs...and ribs...and don't worry 
 we've got veggie stuff too!\n\nCome on out to make some music\, shake you
 r hips\, sip on Griffo's ever-rotating cocktail menu\, and keep the jam a
 live! See you at Thursdays Griffo Distillery! 🎸🥁🎷🍸 #ScottStreetGinJam
  #LiveMusic #GriffoDistillery\n\nAs featured in The Bohemian & Argus Cour
 rier - Thank You Don Lewis & David Templeton!!\n\nPlease RSVP for this FR
 EE\, All Ages Event!
CATEGORIES:featured
X-TKF-FEATURED-IMAGE:https://d3flpus5evl89n.cloudfront.net/66a176f54da645
 42918f1357/697819762c97af2cfcb860f8/scaled_896.jpg
X-TKF-CUSTOM-PREVIEW:Join us every other Thursday for a Jam like no other
 ! 🎶 Scott Street Gin Jam at Griffo Distillery! 🎶 Join us EVERY 1st & 3r
 d Thursday at Griffo Distillery...
