SUMMARY:Polly O'Keary and The Rhythm Method @ The Big Easy
DESCRIPTION:Polly O’Keary and The Rhythm Method are a high‑energy\, award‑winning blues‑rock trio from Seattle\, known for their powerhouse musicianship\, big personalities\, and wildly entertaining live shows. When not touring nationally\, they light up festivals and venues across the Northwest with a fiery mix of Blues\, Rock ’n’ Roll\, R&B\, Soul\, and more. \nThe band has earned national acclaim—including charting releases and recognition from the International Blues Challenge and LA Music Critic—and its members hold multiple Washington Blues Society awards for vocals\, songwriting\, bass\, drums\, and guitar. \nFull bio\, press kit\, media\, and radio coverage are available on the band’s website. www.pollyokeary.com
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/polly-okeary-and-the-rhythm-method-the-big-easy/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/POK-photo-by-Randy-Hiatt-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
