DESCRIPTION:Volunteer on the farm on Wednesdays\, 9am-noon. Tasks typically
  include weeding\, seeding\, mulching\, planting\, and when it's the seaso
 n\, harvesting. It's a great way to get out and help grow fresh\, healthy 
 food for the community.
