SUMMARY: Thursday Sunset Paddle & Party
DESCRIPTION:Start your evening on the Petaluma River with this relaxed mo
 nthly paddle hosted by The Floathouse Petaluma. Launch around 5:30 pm and
  enjoy a casual group paddle through downtown as the evening light settle
 s over the water. We return to the dock about 30 minutes before sunset\, 
 when everyone gathers for simple snacks and conversation on the dock.\n\n
 A perfect after-work outing and a great way to experience downtown Petalu
 ma from the river.\n\n2026 Dates: April 9 • May 14 • June 11 • July 9 • A
 ugust 20 • September 24\n\n$35 kayak or SUP rental for the duration of th
 e paddle\n$10 bring your own board or boat\n\nhttps://book.peek.com/s/b76
