SUMMARY: Downtown Holiday Shopping Stroll
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the season in Downtown Petaluma! Wander through fes
 tively decorated streets\, discover one-of-a-kind gifts in local shops\, 
 and enjoy holiday treats\, cheerful libations\, live music\, and extended
  store hours. All activities will take place inside participating busines
 ses. Whether you’re hunting hens\, shopping for loved ones\, or simply so
 aking in the holiday spirit\, there’s something fun on every corner.\n\nT
 hroughout the day you can enjoy photo ops with Santa & Mrs Claus\, FREE F
 ace painting\, Dancers\, singers\, special holiday promotions & in-store 
 activities\, festive bites and drinks\, live local music\, holiday décor 
 & photo ops\, Holiday Hen Hunt - details can be found HERE https://petalu
 madowntown.com/holiday-hen-hunt \, and much more!\n\nSee the list of part
 icipating businesses offering special holiday activities and treats here 
 https://petalumadowntown.com/holiday-shopping-stroll !
